title: RYM Top 100 Drum & Bass - DnB - Jungle - Techstep LPs 1-50
description:
The top 100 Drum & Bass chart on RateYourMusic, based on its state when I compiled the torrent on 10/12/13 (or 12/10/13 for those of you across the pond). This includes all subgenres, so the margin is wide for the music in this torrent. Though (in my opinion) it's a stretch to call some of these albums drum & bass, they are all impressive albums regardless, so I decided to let the RYM community have the final word on that for simplicity's sake.

tl;dr Congrats! You've just stumbled upon a wide variety of great tunes. Just don't take the genre stuff too seriously and you'll love it.
